<plot>Our Hero, a man by his very nature of a helpful disposition, sets out for his daily walk. On his journey he seeks out those in need to which he might lend whatever assistance they require. But his efforts to aid a disabled man across the street reveal the limits of his patience and show that sometimes cheerful people have the worst breaking points.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074736</url></doc>
